Added color change on laser scan vertices to indicate proximity to the robot.
Basic HUD showing unitless speed and turn rate values. Also added tilt control recalibration.
Added simple GPS display to HUDFragment.
Added connection strength indicator to HUD. Improved GPS display.
Made the HUDFragment fit smaller displays better and added some minor improvements.
Stopped app crashing when screen rotated. For some reason though, the app goes back to the first screen and shuts ros down.
Added documentation to LaserScanLayer, LaserScanFragment, JoystickView and JoystickFragment.
Added missing drawables.

Fixed a bug that caused the app to crash when screen rotated while waiting to connect to a robot.
Fixed minor bug that caused RobotInfos to be created with the same name.
Added some documentation.
Added a simple Unit Test.
Added a simple Instrumentation Test for the RobotChooser.
